---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contacto" description="Cómo escribirle a SaleHoy.">
  <section class="page container-narrow">
    <header class="page__header">
      <span class="meta-label">Contacto</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Escribinos</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        Para opinar, sugerir un tema, corregir un dato, proponer una colaboración, o simplemente charlar.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="contact-options">
      <a href="mailto:hola@salehoy.netlify.app" class="contact-card">
        <span class="meta-label">Mail</span>
        <span class="contact-card__value">hola@salehoy.netlify.app</span>
        <span class="contact-card__hint">Respondemos cada par de días.</span>
      </a>

      <a href="https://instagram.com/salehoyrevista" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-card">
        <span class="meta-label">Instagram</span>
        <span class="contact-card__value">@salehoyrevista</span>
        <span class="contact-card__hint">Donde publicamos primero.</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-note">
      <p>
        <strong>Si te preocupa cómo estás jugando</strong>, hay recursos de ayuda en nuestra página de <a href="/aviso-legal">aviso legal</a>. Por favor, no nos escribas a nosotros: hay profesionales con quien hablar.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page { padding-block: var(--space-3xl); }
  .page__header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
  .page__header .hero-lead { margin-top: var(--space-md); margin-inline: auto; }

  .contact-options {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-block: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .contact-options { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .contact-card:hover { border-color: var(--color-accent-gold); }

  .contact-card__value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-accent-gold);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .contact-card__hint {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .contact-note {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent-red);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .contact-note a {
    color: var(--color-accent-gold);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 0.2em;
  }
</style>
